snippet.title: Kunitsu-Gami: Path of the Goddess - Gameplay Deep Dive
snippet.description:
Dive further into the unique blend of action and strategy in Kunitsu-Gami: Path of the Goddess with this brand new gameplay showcase. 

Kunitsu-Gami: Path of the Goddess releases in 2024 on Xbox Game Pass, Xbox Series X|S, Windows, PlayStation 5 and Steam!
